# Post ->  "/setFeatures"

#### Request Sample:-

{
	"userid" : "a@gmail.com",
	"role" : "Owner",
	"features" : [
		"Add Notice",
		"Update Apartment Key"
		]
}

#### Responce Sample:-  
1. UserIsNotCorrect
{
    "resourceName": "User",
    "fieldName": "UserId",
    "fieldValue": "k@gmail.com",
    "status": "Not Found",
    "message": "User with this userid does not exist"
}
2. Unauthorized
{
    "resourceName": "User",
    "fieldName": "Role",
    "fieldValue": "v@gmail.com",
    "status": "Forbidden",
    "message": "You are not authorized to align roles"
}
3. RoleNotCorrect
{
    "resourceName": "Role",
    "fieldName": "Role name",
    "fieldValue": "Owne",
    "status": "Not Found",
    "message": "Role not supported"
}
4. IfFeatureProvidedIsWrong
{
    "resourceName": "Features",
    "fieldName": "Name",
    "fieldValue": "",
    "status": "Not Found",
    "message": "Some of the features not supported"
}
5. Success
{
    "resourceName": "Features",
    "fieldName": "",
    "fieldValue": "a@gmail.com",
    "status": "success",
    "message": "Feature added to the role"
}


#### Description : -
1. Sets features for the specific user.
